main event: An unidentified object was found in a yard after crashing to the ground, leaving residual materials.
interesting points: The sighting lasted for 15 minutes,The object was described as having a green plastic exterior and being filled with a gel-like substance,Infrared analysis revealed the object was primarily composed of polystyrene,The object appeared to be charred and distorted, possible indications of it being covered in cloth saturated with fuel oil.
sighted object: greenish object with a possibly cotton covering
witness description: Mrs. Frank Wood and Hugh Wood found the object in their backyard.
